title: Can't Run Xseg - "The paging file is too small for this operation to complete"
body:
Trying out DeepFaceLab. Seems to run fine until I try to run Xseg when I get the error shown below. I've moved the installation between C drive and an external and both have the same error. I've also manually increased the paging file size for both drives though I'm not sure how much the app is trying to use. Anyone else find a fix?
